(42, 12, 22, 40, 6, 25, 34, 'Take no thought for your life', 'Concern for Daily Needs', 'Both passages emphasize the idea of not worrying about daily necessities such as food and clothing. They highlight God''s provision for creation, encouraging trust in His care rather than anxiety over material needs.', 'theme', 0.412, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini')
